Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我这种小人物纠缠合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事态似乎愈发严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少看不起我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙也能应付吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个无趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就借你点…力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要控制…力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量的…控制…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没…结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信…你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是九尾化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很危险 抓紧去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…如果不制止那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 请交给我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我虽然被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但曾经也是村子的守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护这里…保护巨坑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭哥哥现在的体力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能抵达目的地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了…带我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法兹 不可以再挑食了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算难吃也不能挑肥拣瘦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要增强体力 保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰德 你最大 要振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家有困难要互相帮助哦 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小空 要好好照顾大家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照看好米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后或许会经历很多酸甜苦辣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做大家的支柱哦 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时扇了你一记耳光 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只有米娜察觉到鸣人哥哥的异样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能理解你…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后也许会很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不要逃避 坚强起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和哥哥还有大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚强地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是短暂的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但和大家在一起真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相当幸福的时光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位 孩子们就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能死里逃生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那无论如何都要活下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 是音律
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据那家伙说是按特定顺序排列的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的顺序呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 就是米娜哼得曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子很早前就一直哼着的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩尽 杀绝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 完全失去自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快爬上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 好像脱臼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 快帮我治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 可是九尾的力量太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道能束缚它多久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 得赶紧想其他办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别认输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经有准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我决不会放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我来 还是赶紧让天之矛停下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我再次看着最爱之人落下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:17:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一直 一直都喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才拼命抓住你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我再也不会放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果放手的话 还不如一起掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是从那时起对你念念不忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我比你高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你变秃 变胖 变得迟钝 变得懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你对我敬而远之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 我还是一直喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 谁去保护那些孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子的未来只有靠你拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要守护 想要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的人们 我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助爸爸和妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信着 相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信正义的力量 相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:19:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护好那些孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱着你…爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 赶紧阻止那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少捣乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.45,0:24:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.06,0:24:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.79,0:24:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你救我一命 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.16,0:24:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 真的感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.69,0:29:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.15,0:29:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然用秽土转生让人柱力们复活
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.10,0:29:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.79,0:29:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争由我来阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.40,0:29:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人能够感知敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.78,0:29:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样他就必须得出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.68,0:29:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不出我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.55,0:29:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日起 千手的火之意志将要消亡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.38,0:29:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.03,0:29:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 参战
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.60,0:29:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于轮到我出场了
